{"tid":2374374,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"上海新增3宗本土確診病例　其中2人來自不同醫院","createTime":"2021-01-21T07:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T07:45:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"011f4e7f6eef72320961fb38f941986148a8d410","tid":2374374,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:37:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571582-20210121.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571582-20210121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcBR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=af20baae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1571582-20210121.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5bb79c11\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1571582-20210121.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n上海新增3宗來自本土的新型肺炎確診病例，是當地近兩個月以來，再次出現本土感染。<br />\n<br />\n其中兩名男患者分別來自兩間醫院，一人是復旦大學附屬腫瘤醫院的外判員工，另一人就是上海交通大學醫學院附屬仁濟醫院人員，兩人都是在當地對醫院展開的例行檢測中確診，住在同一小區；其中一人的一名密切接觸者，今日凌晨亦確診。<br />\n<br />\n上海市相關部門已經組成專家組，展開流行病學調查，對追蹤到的密切接觸者進行檢測及集中隔離觀察。"},{"pid":"87a20cd89cd586683d1f0a0068b66bd6c37e82f7","tid":2374374,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:39:27.000Z","msg":"仲扮野"},{"pid":"93cb42df0ffa2a2066644a6bd4ddc2d7b25d1826","tid":2374374,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:45:15.000Z","msg":"上海緊貼香港"}]}